# TWRP Device Tree for ZTE Changxing 50 (P720S16)
Welcome to the TWRP (Team Win Recovery Project) device tree repository for the **ZTE Changxing 50 (codename: P720S16)**.

## Device Specifications
| Feature | Details |
| ---- | ---- |
| Codename | P720S16 |
| Model | ZTE Changxing 50 |
| Chipset | Unisoc T606 |
| RAM | 4GB / 6GB |
| Storage | 64GB / 128GB |
| Battery | 5000mAh Li-Po |
| Display | 6.52 inches, IPS LCD, 720 x 1600 pixels |
| Rear Camera | 13MP + 2MP |
| Front Camera | 5MP |
| Platform | Unisoc (Spreadtrum) |

## Device picture

![ZTE Changxing 50](https://oss.ztedevices.com/prod/cn/2023/09/20230920458.jpg)

## Compatibility
- This device tree is built for **TWRP 12.1 / 13.0**
- Compatible with ZTE Changxing 50 (P720S16) global variants
- Supports Android 12 / Android 13 stock firmware

## Features
### Working
- ✅ ADB access
- ✅ Decryption (stock Android 12/13)
- ✅ Touchscreen
- ✅ Internal storage / SD card mount
- ✅ Backup & Restore
- ✅ Flashing ZIP/IMG files
- ✅ Reboot to system/recovery/bootloader
- ✅ Vibration
- ✅ USB-OTG

### Not Working
- ❌ None (Full functional TWRP)

## Build Instructions
### 1. Initialize TWRP Source
```bash
repo init --depth=1 -u https://github.com/minimal-manifest-twrp/platform_manifest_twrp_aosp.git -b twrp-12.1
```

### 2. Sync Source
```bash
repo sync -j$(nproc --all) --force-sync
```

### 3. Clone Device Tree
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/android_device_zte_P720S16.git device/zte/P720S16
```

### 4. Build Recovery Image
```bash
source build/envsetup.sh
lunch twrp_P720S16-eng
mka recoveryimage
```

## Output Location
After successful build, the recovery image will be generated at:
```
out/target/product/P720S16/recovery.img
```

## Installation Instructions
### Prerequisites
- Unlocked bootloader
- Fastboot installed on PC
- USB debugging & OEM unlocking enabled

### Flash via Fastboot
```bash
fastboot flash recovery recovery.img
fastboot reboot recovery
```

## Notes
- This device tree is **only for P720S16** (ZTE Changxing 50)
- Do not flash on any other ZTE/Unisoc devices
- Backup all data before flashing custom recovery
- Decryption requires stock Android 12/13 keystore

